    <item>
      <title>全球交易价值创十年新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-19/global-deal-values-hit-decade-low-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社汇编的数据显示，今年假期期间，并购及相关交易的价值下降了大约四分之一，至 2.7 万亿美元。这是自 2013 年以来最低的年度总数。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-19/global-deal-values-hit-decade-low-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 19:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rite Aid 同意与阿片类药物受害者、债权人进行调解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/rite-aid-agrees-to-mediation-with-opioid-victims-creditor-panel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产的连锁药店 Rite Aid Corp. 同意开始与级别较低的债权人进行法院监督的调解，其中包括指责该公司造成美国阿片类药物成瘾危机的团体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/rite-aid-agrees-to-mediation-with-opioid-victims-creditor-panel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 19:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国和德国周三将就财政规则达成欧盟协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/france-and-germany-expect-eu-deal-on-fiscal-rules-on-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟两个最大经济体的财政部长表示，他们有信心在周三的虚拟会议上与欧盟同行就新的财政规则达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-19/france-and-germany-expect-eu-deal-on-fiscal-rules-on-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 19:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
